folders created after installing jenkins:
-----------------------------------------
nodes, logs, usercontent, workflowlibs, users, jobs, finger prints, secrets, tools, caches, workspace, plugins, updates
======================================================================================================================================
how to configure webhooks for jenkins:
-------------------------------------

got to repo>settings>webhooks> give jenkins url with github-webhook/

go to jenkins job > source code management > repository url> GitHub hook trigger for GITScm polling

======================================================================================================================================

how many ways we can trigger jenkins:
------------------------------------
trigger builds remotely
build after other projects are build
build periodically 
GitHub hook trigger for GITScm polling
Poll SCM
